#!/usr/bin/env bash

# Display help overview for the ghjk plugin

cat << 'EOF'
asdf-ghjk - asdf plugin for ghjk (development environment manager)

ABOUT GHJK:
  ghjk is a modern development environment manager that provides:
  - Unified package management across npm, PyPI, crates.io, and more
  - TypeScript-based task automation powered by Deno
  - Reproducible POSIX environments for development, CI/CD, and containers

INSTALLATION:
  asdf plugin add ghjk https://github.com/Hyperpolymath/asdf-ghjk.git
  asdf install ghjk latest
  asdf global ghjk latest

USAGE:
  asdf list all ghjk              # List all available versions
  asdf install ghjk <version>     # Install a specific version
  asdf install ghjk latest        # Install the latest version
  asdf global ghjk <version>      # Set global version
  asdf local ghjk <version>       # Set local version
  asdf current ghjk               # Show current version
  asdf uninstall ghjk <version>   # Uninstall a version

EXAMPLES:
  # Install and use latest ghjk
  asdf install ghjk latest
  asdf global ghjk latest
  ghjk --version

  # Initialize a project with ghjk
  mkdir my-project && cd my-project
  ghjk init ts

  # Use ghjk to manage your development environment
  ghjk env              # Activate environment
  ghjk run <task>       # Run defined tasks

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES:
  GITHUB_API_TOKEN      Set to avoid GitHub API rate limits

SUPPORTED PLATFORMS:
  - Linux (x86_64, aarch64)
  - macOS (x86_64, arm64/M1+)

DOCUMENTATION:
  Plugin:  https://github.com/Hyperpolymath/asdf-ghjk
  ghjk:    https://github.com/metatypedev/ghjk
  asdf:    https://asdf-vm.com

TROUBLESHOOTING:
  - Check GitHub API rate limits if list/install fails
  - Ensure required dependencies are installed: git, curl, tar, unzip, zstd
  - Run with ASDF_DEBUG=1 for verbose output

SUPPORT:
  Issues:  https://github.com/Hyperpolymath/asdf-ghjk/issues
  Docs:    https://github.com/Hyperpolymath/asdf-ghjk/blob/main/README.md
EOF
